data.description:
Beautiful custom new home with upgrades throughout. The spacious kitchen offers double wall ovens and walk in pantry. Open floor plan provides a formal dining area and lots of extra storage. Master bathroom has an extra large walk in shower with an extended area to dry off. 
Beautifully landscaped backyard for hosting friends and family.
Plenty of room for all of your toys in the extended RV garage.  Come see this gem before its gone!
